# Configuration file for the sink particles that represent star clusters
# Written by Shyam Harimohan Menon (2022).
#
# Main references:
#   Menon et al. (2022, MNRAS 512, 401)
#   Menon et al. (2022, MNRAS 517, 1313)
#   Menon et al. (2023, MNRAS 521, 5160)

D          cluster_lumpermass  Luminosity per unit mass of star cluster in FUV band. EUV value taken to be 40% of this (appropriate for stellar populations)  
PARAMETER  cluster_lumpermass  REAL  1.7e3

D          cluster_type        Flag for type of luminosity per-unit mass: 1 - constant value, 2 - SLUG fit from Kim et al. (2016)
PARAMETER  cluster_type        INTEGER 1

D          cluster_imffactor   Factor by which to multiply L/M to account for IMF variations at the high-mass end. Default = 1 (Salpeter)
PARAMETER  cluster_imffactor   REAL  1.0

# Sink particle properties: Luminosity of FUV photons and EUV photon rate
PARTICLEPROP  LUMFUV   REAL
PARTICLEPROP  EUVRATE  REAL
